{"tid":1452370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請下載抖音 一人一留言","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:17:39.000Z","uid":27133,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3360157eafe14f2d252524ffaf54267cc0a52665","tid":1452370,"uid":27133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:02:58.000Z","msg":"我發現好多野做出黎都係旨在拍到個畫面出黎然後作故仔比大陸人睇，一個片可以有成千成萬個讚，一個留言都有幾萬個讚，睇既人可能有上億，有d留言我見到會有質疑，只要我地一人一個留言，屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都冇所謂，對我地有利既留言就讚，作故事既難度就會大大增加，從而影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />部署<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3AMMB3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3AMMB3.png&h=6b21e174&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ama1Avp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAma1Avp.png&h=b9c8e38b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6EM4yg4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6EM4yg4.png&h=de330044&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8c9f75c0bcfc20eda2a57f9c575bd6fc8939c0f","tid":1452370,"uid":27133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045066479078a5a5bc1901c8993b2e213e24c055","tid":1452370,"uid":27133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f0b7238e84e17f36eab04d0d6a93cac3466596","tid":1452370,"uid":27133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bc180843943b12ac027ab4a7a41d33d76c3b07","tid":1452370,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:06:28.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n輸出革命"},{"pid":"a7a196549a02d58159eeee3129f6204c56889